Package org.blockchainnative.fabric.metadata

Class FabricParameterInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.ParameterInfo
      • org.blockchainnative.fabric.metadata.FabricParameterInfo
  • public class FabricParameterInfo
extends ParameterInfo
    Holds additional information about a parameter of a smart contract method.

    It is recommended to use FabricContractInfoBuilder to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    FabricContractInfoBuilder
